  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hygienic conditions for the blinds at IIP &#x201C;Orhei&#x201D; social enterprise</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Voda a sanita pre sicialny podnik &quot;Orhei&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Projekt je zameran&#xFD; na zlep&#x161;enie hygienick&#xFD;ch podmienok v soci&#xE1;lnom podniku, ktor&#xFD; zamestn&#xE1;va &#x13E;ud&#xED; so zn&#xED;&#x17E;enou schopnos&#x165;ou videnia. Tento podnik m&#xE1; neadekv&#xE1;tne podmienky z h&#x13E;adiska vody a sanit&#xE1;cie- toalety nies&#xFA; k dispoz&#xED;cii a potrebn&#xE9; je pou&#x17E;&#xED;va&#x165; toaletu umiestnen&#xFA; mimo budovy a vodu je potrebn&#xE9; nosi&#x165; zo studne. Pomocou projektu bud&#xFA; zrekon&#x161;truovan&#xE9; star&#xE9; nepou&#x17E;&#xED;van&#xE9; toalety v budove a bude zaveden&#xFD; vodovod z existuj&#xFA;cej studne.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to solve the problem of hygienic conditions for the blind people at the social Enterprise Moldova Blind Union. Direct beneficiaries will be 30 people, employees of the social enterprise and its visitors.</narrative>
  </description>
